{"tid":457240,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我同女朋友散既原因唔係有第三者","createTime":"2017-11-03T16:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T00:33:27.000Z","uid":122694,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d861ef4f4a0bdbd1b89f8134501677a1f4c57b","tid":457240,"uid":122694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"已拍拖約2年 <br />\n佢話想放低 冇左熱戀期個種feel<br />\n又覺得好難行到落去好遠<br />\n我不斷解釋話每段感情既新鮮感<br />\n到某日都會冇而變做感情 好好相處 <br />\n咁樣冇可能有段長久愛情<br />\n<br />\n若冷靜期過左 大家都放低曬 <br />\n有一天我想追返佢 會唔會有可能<br />\n我覺得搵到一個人自己能去愛 係好珍貴 <br />\n我知愛情係要兩邊付出 <br />\n但係我知道點都好 我都會係佢身邊 <br />\n有時真係好心酸<br />\n可以點 <br />\n了解一個新既人會好辛苦 <br />\n同埋覺得自己都冇力氣去咁做"},{"pid":"14a97fa50546e0eda3684e1c621342308b3ad29a","tid":457240,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"放過人啦"},{"pid":"d504b54c5e3d3bf0b2456c32bfe71ca9874eb97f","tid":457240,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"講多無謂，行動最實際。。"},{"pid":"a37728590626b85511c9a9795b01f27c8eef1666","tid":457240,"uid":1833,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"算喇<br />\n佢只係對厭咗你<br />\n想搵過件<br />\n你講幾多野都係哂氣<br />\n真係愛一個人<br />\n係唔會介意熱戀期嘅長短<br />\n只會在意大家嘅感情<br />\n所以你都係搵過個真係愛你㗎喇"},{"pid":"80e722f60a2c14b3f5414ec484991e07b7a8a96b","tid":457240,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得啲人話淡左就散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但愛情最終都會變成感情<br />\n因對一個人太耐點都會悶<br />\n如果唔係咪結左婚都會好易離婚<br />\n點會一生一世"},{"pid":"e633d4ee9fe70f1bc559cbc96356f25e2a435459","tid":457240,"uid":154231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T22:12:33.000Z","msg":"我咪被分手果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 提出分手既人根本就係唔夠愛,講咩都係藉口,乜野好大壓力好辛苦唔開心,咪就係唔再愛先會有既感覺,都唔知扮乜偉人,食完人隻豬同初初既承諾去左邊？  大家屌醒我啦,我岩岩仲唔知醜搵人"},{"pid":"d65721af5592481414d6120d7d2080d1ab790a24","tid":457240,"uid":30808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T22:24:37.000Z","msg":"冇可能一齊翻<br />\n佢只係對其他人有新鮮感/未玩夠<br />\n利申 過來人"},{"pid":"c95ecc63878e9d5447758a2e538d94495019be55","tid":457240,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:37:22.000Z","msg":"放過自己啦<br />\n唔係鍾意第二個點會講得出感情淡咗<br />\n<br />\n利申拍咗好多年拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb95c17ffe0382dfe3f31bbf999ea6209c940dce","tid":457240,"uid":59702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:48:45.000Z","msg":"我早你兩個月被分手 我都好似你咁傻仔以為冇第三者 分左手兩個禮拜左右 我朋友見到佢拖住第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0733225780fe4de83093903a9d20c4ae073ce0","tid":457240,"uid":150954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:58:58.000Z","msg":"扮乜野，想大家好落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad55482d640894512a2641d93682c0358f2c832","tid":457240,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮乜野，想大家好落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又未必護眼嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d709f9742a28a0e39a7eeceb5ac6bd93ab1316b","tid":457240,"uid":156541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:33:27.000Z","msg":"好想要時光機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}